    "This indicates that Subspace Boosting is not highly sensitive to the exact threshold, provided it is large enough.",
    "We therefore chose β = 0.2 for our experiments to ensure robust spectral flattening.",
    "Unless otherwise stated, all ablations are performed by merging all 12 fine-tuned variants and sweeping the corresponding method-specific hyperparameters.",
